&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the SVP, Product, you’ll work with editorial, marketing, audience, analytics, and business development teams to identify and prioritize product needs. A goal-oriented mindset, energy for problem solving, and bias for action are essential for success in this role. Bonus points if you have demonstrated experience in digital news, working with editorial products, and building responsive web and mobile app products (Android and iOS).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
